    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/868b47717969bee90d7b9c8373044045.avif?t=1762470053\" width=780 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年轻的日本发明家骏雄两年前来到法国，定居于宁静的乡村。某天，他突然收到了一封由尼古拉·特斯拉亲笔签名的邀请函，邀他前往巴黎埃菲尔铁塔参加十年一度的科学盛会。骏雄满怀期待奔赴巴黎，然而，在特斯拉的开幕演讲中，会场突然陷入一片黑暗。当灯光再度亮起——特斯拉竟在大庭广众之下神秘消失！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >警方展开全面调查的同时，骏雄与机智的爱犬阿尔皮娜也毅然踏上追寻真相之路。决心揭开这场诡异失踪案件背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/562c5d04a99a71f61ffb22a2e2df6dc4.avif?t=1762470053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/d2db4410f6ca18842e8d0994b79143d3.avif?t=1762470053\" width=780 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作以谜题为核心，来推进故事流程与剧情。玩家将探索精心绘制的巴黎，在各个场景中和角色对话，或者与场景中的物件互动。每个角色或者互动物件身上可能都藏着一个谜题，解开谜题后就可以推进下一步剧情，或者获得新的线索。一个个谜题最终串联起一个精彩的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/24bc24e4d53cc238baf38c977164c9ae.avif?t=1762470053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/099cea6d6f9d0737e69f881f748ec9ce.avif?t=1762470053\" width=780 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设计了丰富多样的谜题，每一道都趣味十足，全方位考验你的观察力、推理能力和逻辑思维。如果你在解题过程中遭遇瓶颈，也可以随时查看左下角的提示卷轴，不用担心卡关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/4bfb07ffbbab37dc42d882265ee528d1.poster.avif?t=1762470053\" width=800 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/4bfb07ffbbab37dc42d882265ee528d1.webm?t=1762470053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/4bfb07ffbbab37dc42d882265ee528d1.mp4?t=1762470053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中并非所有人都会对你坦诚相待。有些人会不断的编织谎言来掩盖内心深处的秘密。你需要仔细分析他们的证词抓住他们对话中的逻辑漏洞，将”证据“化作子弹击碎他们的心理防线，从他们的口中获取推动剧情的关键线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/a046967364dadbd8de9d8f6e32192413.poster.avif?t=1762470053\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/a046967364dadbd8de9d8f6e32192413.webm?t=1762470053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/a046967364dadbd8de9d8f6e32192413.mp4?t=1762470053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/abcff3085fbe6f6c2ffb1e7d3f6ef2fd.avif?t=1762470053\" width=780 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《特斯拉之谜》采用精美的卡通画风，融合蒸汽朋克的机械元素与新艺术的优雅曲线，营造出梦幻而独特的架空巴黎。游戏中每一个场景都手绘细腻，从埃菲尔铁塔的宏伟到乡村小巷的宁静，都充满生动细节。角色设计可爱而富有个性，结合流畅的动画效果，让玩家仿佛置身于一幅妙趣横生的卡通画卷之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/24e9440cb402f2a4daf11a3b5673a527.poster.avif?t=1762470053\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/24e9440cb402f2a4daf11a3b5673a527.webm?t=1762470053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
